summary: Are you sick of that broken-down little house outside of whiterun. This is a small mod that repairs the broken-down house. Sorry that you cant enter the house but this is my first mod.
descriptionHtml:
It replaces the broken house with a farmhouse. I made this mod because i hated looking at that broken house when going on an adventure. I\'m sorry about not being aloud enter the house and that there is no images because i don\'t know how to upload them. But it is my first mod, hope you enjoy

Thanks to Dilpickle3899 for the pic
author: simell
